Calm and very hot.  Not as many weeds in the shallow parts of the lake this year.  Normally there are a lot.
D.O. 8.4   SECCHI 1.5   TEMP.80.5 AT 6FT DOWN  SUNNY DAY NO WIND LOTS OF GEESE SWIMMING SOME WEEDS GROWING ALGE IS PRESENT BUT PEOPLE WERE SWIMMING THE DAY WE TESTED
Just got done raining at 10:00 am.  Looks like pretty good weed growth along the shore line.  Water is still brownish/green.  Dont see any dead fish.
